# ovh_vps_change_contact

Manages contact changes for an OVHcloud VPS service.

## Example Usage

{{tffile "examples/resources/vps_change_contact/example_1.tf"}}

## Argument Reference

The following arguments are supported:

* `service_name` - (Required) The service_name of your VPS.
* `contact_admin` - (Optional) NIC handle of the admin contact to set.
* `contact_billing` - (Optional) NIC handle of the billing contact to set.
* `contact_tech` - (Optional) NIC handle of the technical contact to set.

## Attributes Reference

(See generated docs/resources/vps_change_contact.md for the full attribute list.)

The following attributes are exported:

* `id` - The ID of the contact change task.
